    "title": "CONCOR Consulting Pvt Ltd is Hiring: Warehouse Manager (Principal)",
    "description": "An exciting career opportunity awaits you at CONCOR Consulting Pvt Ltd. We are on the lookout for a dedicated Warehouse Manager to strengthen our Pune-based team.\n\nAbout CONCOR Consulting Pvt Ltd:\nCONCOR Consulting Pvt Ltd is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Manage reverse logistics and return merchandise authorization\n• Prepare MIS reports on delivery performance and SLA adherence\n• Manage relationships with third-party logistics providers\n• Implement warehouse management systems (WMS) and track KPIs\n• Track shipments in real-time and resolve delivery exceptions\n• Conduct periodic vendor audits and evaluate logistics partners\n• Manage a fleet of vehicles and coordinate with drivers\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Ed / M.Ed from a recognized institution\n• 10-15 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in ERP Systems\n• Proficiency in Freight Forwarding\n• Proficiency in SAP SCM\n• Proficiency in Data Analytics\n• Proficiency in Reverse Logistics\n• Proficiency in Vendor Management\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in WMS\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Learning & development budget\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Salary Range: 20 LPA - 40 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Pune, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with CONCOR Consulting Pvt Ltd!",
